   "text": "- attorney posts case handoff in slack -> case exists, intakes sent\n- client emails the firm -> agent investigates, drafts reply\n- @yunaki <task> -> agent works the task with tools\n- nothing sends without a human pressing approve",
   "fontSize": 16,
   "fontFamily": 1,
   "textAlign": "left",
   "verticalAlign": "top",
