   "updated": 1,
   "link": null,
   "locked": false,
   "text": "* agentic where it matters, code-owned where it counts\n  (model picks tools; code owns grants, budget, transcript)\n* null over guess (agent asks in thread, never invents)\n* no PII in logs/events (hashes + counts); fictional demo cast\n* LIVE_MODE=false default -> outbox, never a real client\n* every send: DraftAction -> approve -> sendgate (schema-enforced)",
   "fontSize": 16,
   "fontFamily": 1,
   "textAlign": "left",
   "verticalAlign": "top",
   "containerId": null,
   "originalText": "* agentic where it matters, code-owned where it counts\n  (model picks tools; code owns grants, budget, transcript)\n* null over guess (agent asks in thread, never invents)\n* no PII in logs/events (hashes + counts); fictional demo cast\n* LIVE_MODE=false default -> outbox, never a real client\n* every send: DraftAction -> approve -> sendgate (schema-enforced)",
   "autoResize": true,
   "lineHeight": 1.25
  },
